.SH NAME
pico-test \- Perform a test authentication using the
.BR pico-continuous (8) 
service.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B pico-test
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
This manual page documents briefly the
.B pico-test
program.
.PP
The 
.B pico-test
program can be used to test the 
.BR pico-continuous (8)
service. 
It will send dbus messages to the service requesting to authenticate, 
display the returned QR code on the command line and return the result of 
any authentication that the service subsequently performs.
.PP
This allows authentication to be tested without having to go via the PAM 
interface. 
To test the service using the PAM interface, something like 
.BR pamtester (1)
can be used instead.
.PP
